      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just walking in circles lately. every time i think i finally figured things out, i just end up back at the exact same spot. another failed job, another person leaving, another month of feeling like nothing changed. it’s just the same loop over and over again and i’m so tired of it.",
